title: Surveillance
comment: it may have trackers, listening devices etc that can be used for surveillance by the goverment

title: unfair
comment: some people may not be eligible for one who want one, or cant afford one, or live in a country with low standards of healthcare and cant get one. there may be a kind of discrimination against people with/without them, such as applying for jobs, you may get turned down without the implant.

title: useful
comment: some people could really be helped by this, such as people with sleep problems, soldiers, long haul truckers, athletes (if it is not banned) etc

title: Not secure
comment: Someone could hack the device and shut you down remotely. there could be bugs and it could activate at the wrong time, for example while driving

title: unnecesary
comment: we have survived this long without the chip

title: interesting
comment: it would be a fascinating thing rom a technical side

title: Painful
comment: there procedure to get it installed may be painful or there may be side effects later
